://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Elon-Musk-Leadership-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1891px) 100vw, 1891px" /></p><p>由于知名人士的投诉，一场旨在纪念<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elon-musk">埃隆·马斯克</a>和鲁珀特·默多克等人的活动已被取消。</p><p> 3 月 13 日宣布，今年奥珀曼基金会大法官露丝·巴德·金斯伯格领导奖的获奖者包括马斯克、默多克、玛莎·斯图尔特、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sylvester-stallone">西尔维斯特·史泰龙</a>和迈克尔·米尔肯。</p><p>这位特斯拉创始人和前福克斯新闻首席执行官的加入引发了金斯伯格家族成员的强烈反对。金斯伯格的儿子詹姆斯批评了该基金会，称他的母亲会对获奖者感到“震惊”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3603548" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3603548" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3603548" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ruth-Bader-Ginsburg-Elon-Musk.jpg" alt="露丝·巴德·金斯伯格" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ruth-Bader-Ginsburg-Elon-Musk.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ruth-Bader-Ginsburg-Elon-Musk-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ruth-Bader-Ginsburg-Elon-Musk-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ruth-Bader-Ginsburg-Elon-Musk-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ruth-Bader-Ginsburg-Elon-Musk-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ruth-Bader-Ginsburg-Elon-Musk-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3603548" class="wp-caption-text">露丝·巴德·金斯伯格于 2019 年 9 月 12 日在华盛顿特区。图片来源：盖蒂/汤姆·布伦纳/盖蒂图片社拍摄</figcaption></figure><p>金斯伯格告诉<a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2024/03/17/politics/ruth-bader-ginsburg-son-award-rupert-murdoch-elon-musk/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>美国有线电视新闻网</em></a>：“当你想到努力创建一个更加公正的社会时，这当然是妈妈的最终目标，你可能会想到这些姓氏。”</p><p>他称这一消息是“对[他]母亲记忆的亵渎”，并说：“我认为她会感到震惊。”</p><p>昨天（3月18日）<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barbra-streisand">芭芭拉·史翠珊</a>在 Instagram 上表达了对金斯伯格家族的支持，并与他们一起谴责了颁奖典礼获奖者的选择。</p><p>回顾去年获得最高法院大法官索尼娅·索托马约尔的荣誉，史翠珊写道：“金斯伯格大法官和索托马约尔大法官是两位最受尊敬的女性榜样，她们对民主价值观、特别是妇女权利的承诺是无与伦比的。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4quvPaL4fg/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.